1. Introduction
---------------

A full description of Enterprise-Class Event logging can be found at:

  http://evlog.sourceforge.net/

Not all of the features described in the specification have been
provided.  For a list of these features, see the following:

  http://evlog.sourceforge.net/not_yet_available.html
  
	
2. How to install
------------------

See the INSTALL file.



3. Known Bugs
-------------

See bug tracker on the project page for more details.

530006   Forwarding of syslog msgs = xdm failure
         (This problem has not been observed on Red Hat 8.0
          nor SuSE SLES8 (UL 1.0)
586100   ppc64: evlview fails with long, pointer


4. License 
----------

The kernel patch is licensed under the GNU General Public License (GPL)
Version 2, June 1991.  The full text of the GPL is located at:

evlog/kernel/GPL

The evlogd daemon is also licensed under the GPL.

---

The user library is licensed under the GNU Lesser Public License (LGPL)
Version 2.1, February 1999.  The full text of the LGPL is located at:

evlog/user/LGPL


5. Latest Version
-----------------

1.6.0



6. Change History
-----------------

See the CHANGES file.



7. Reporting Bugs
-----------------
If you encounter a bug, please submit it to the project bug list,
located on the project page:

   https://sourceforge.net/projects/evlog/



